# Forward-looking placeholder ONLY.
#
# The read-only logger phase needs NO credentials on either venue:
#   - Kalshi: the order book endpoint is public (no auth).
#   - Polymarket US: market data is public via `new PolymarketUS()` (no keys).
#
# The variables below are reserved for the FUTURE execution phase. They are
# names only — do NOT populate them in this phase, and never commit a real .env.
#
# When PM US credentials are eventually generated: the secret key is shown
# ONCE at generation time. Back it up in a secret manager immediately; it
# cannot be retrieved again, and it must never be committed to git.

POLYMARKET_KEY_ID=
POLYMARKET_SECRET_KEY=
